00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:03.780
The next type of analysis we're
going to talk about is segmentation.

00:00:03.780 --> 00:00:06.280
Segmentation is the process
of grouping data together.

00:00:07.490 --> 00:00:10.940
Groups can be simple, such as customers
who have purchased different items.

00:00:10.940 --> 00:00:14.490
To more complex segmentation techniques,
where you identify stores that

00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:16.949
are similar based upon
the demographics of their customers.

00:00:18.225 --> 00:00:20.900
Rob Light,
one of our experts in segmentation,

00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:24.100
has dedicated an entire course
to segmentation and grouping

